 ARRAY['Seven-figure annual contracts - accessible only to large enterprises with significant AI budgets', 'Platform complexity requires dedicated ML engineering and IT resources to operate effectively', 'Sales cycle is long - expect 6-18 months from first contact to live deployment', 'Less nimble than pure-play predictive maintenance vendors for single use case deployments'],
