('landing-ai', 'Landing AI', 'Visual AI platform for manufacturing inspection built by the team behind deeplearning.ai',
 E'Landing AI is an AI company founded by Andrew Ng that specializes in applying computer vision to manufacturing quality inspection and visual AI problems in industrial settings. The company''s flagship platform, LandingLens, is a visual AI development tool that enables manufacturing engineers to build, train, and deploy custom deep learning inspection models without a machine learning background - using a browser-based annotation and training workflow that compresses model development from months to days.\n\nLandingLens supports defect detection, object classification, counting, and measurement tasks across factory inspection applications. The platform''s active learning feature prioritizes which images to label next, minimizing the annotation burden while maximizing model accuracy improvement. Models deploy to edge devices in the factory, standard industrial cameras, and cloud endpoints, giving flexibility to match the deployment to the production line''s connectivity and latency requirements. For manufacturers who have struggled to implement AI inspection because of the perceived need for data science expertise, LandingLens provides a credible path to production deployment with process engineers in the lead role.\n\nLanding AI also provides AI transformation consulting services that draw on Andrew Ng''s deep learning expertise to help manufacturing companies build internal AI capabilities rather than remaining dependent on vendors. The combination of a practical software platform and strategic AI advisory has made Landing AI a trusted partner for Fortune 500 manufacturers approaching AI adoption. In 2026, Landing AI has expanded LandingLens to support video-based inspection and multi-sensor fusion alongside standard image inspection. Pricing is enterprise and structured around deployment scale and support requirements.',
 'https://landing.ai', 'https://landing.ai',
 'paid', false, 0, 4.6, 1580, false, true, false,
 ARRAY['computer-vision', 'quality-inspection', 'manufacturing'],
 ARRAY['LandingLens enables process engineers to build AI inspection models without ML expertise', 'Active learning minimizes annotation burden while accelerating model accuracy improvement', 'Flexible deployment to edge, cloud, or camera endpoints for diverse factory environments', 'AI transformation advisory from Andrew Ng''s team builds internal capabilities alongside the software'],
 ARRAY['Enterprise pricing - no self-serve or free tier for evaluation', 'Custom defect detection models still require several hundred labeled images minimum to train effectively', 'Edge deployment requires compatible industrial cameras and computing hardware', 'Advisory services are premium-priced and not included in base software licensing'],
