('relimetrics', 'Relimetrics', 'AI visual quality control for automotive and aerospace manufacturing inspection',
 E'Relimetrics is an AI-powered visual quality control platform designed specifically for the high-precision inspection requirements of automotive and aerospace manufacturing. The platform combines industrial computer vision with AI models trained on the complex, safety-critical defect types that matter in vehicle bodies, structural components, and aerospace parts - surface anomalies, dimensional deviations, weld quality, and assembly verification at tolerances that human visual inspection cannot consistently achieve at production speeds.\n\nRelimetrics deploys as an end-to-end inspection system: the company works with customers on camera and lighting integration, trains defect detection models on customer-specific parts and defect libraries, deploys to edge computing hardware on the production line, and provides ongoing model management as product variants and defect profiles evolve. The platform generates structured inspection records for each part including defect images, classification results, and disposition, creating the quality audit trail that automotive and aerospace customers need for traceability and regulatory compliance.\n\nThe platform is particularly strong in weld inspection - a defect category where traditional non-AI vision systems have historically struggled because weld bead morphology varies too much for rule-based detection. In 2026, Relimetrics has expanded from visual-only inspection to multi-modal quality assessment combining camera, laser profilometer, and ultrasound data in a unified defect analysis model. Deployments are primarily in Europe and North America at Tier 1 and Tier 2 automotive suppliers and aerospace component manufacturers. Pricing is project-based with recurring software licensing; contact sales for current rates.',
 'https://relimetrics.com', 'https://relimetrics.com',
 'paid', false, 0, 4.2, 820, false, false, false,
 ARRAY['quality-inspection', 'computer-vision', 'manufacturing'],
 ARRAY['Specialized in automotive and aerospace inspection tolerances that general vision tools cannot meet', 'Weld inspection capability handles the morphological variation that defeats rule-based vision systems', 'Full audit trail per part with defect images and classification for regulatory compliance', 'Multi-modal inspection combining camera, laser, and ultrasound data in one platform (2026)'],
 ARRAY['Vertical-specific - limited value outside automotive and aerospace manufacturing contexts', 'Full deployment requires significant hardware integration work at the production line', 'Smaller vendor than Cognex or Landing AI - smaller ecosystem and fewer pre-built integrations', 'Model retraining is required when new product variants or defect types are introduced'],
 ARRAY['Automated surface defect detection on body panels, structural components, and safety-critical parts', 'Weld quality inspection for automotive chassis and aerospace structural assembly lines', 'Quality traceability record generation for compliance with IATF 16949 and AS9100 requirements'],
