 ARRAY['Inspection speed has limits on very high-rate production lines (above 300 parts per minute)', 'Model accuracy depends on image quality - lighting and camera positioning require care during setup', 'Less suited to multi-sensor or dimensional inspection vs visual defect detection', 'Smaller vendor with limited enterprise support infrastructure compared to Cognex or Landing AI'],
